headline: Pine Labs, Wynn Resorts price target, Tradeweb downgrade
summary: Yahoo Finance anchor Josh Lipton tracks Thursday's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute, including the PayPal-backed (PYPL) Pine Labs seeking to raise $700 million in its IPO, Wynn Resorts (WYNN) getting a price target boost, and shares of Tradeweb Markets (TW) receiving a downgrade. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
